OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778655959
OL,3,CPerson rescued after getting stuck
OL,4,Cwaist deep in mud near Cornish beach
OL,6,FA person had to be rescued after
OL,7,Fgetting stuck in the mud at the
OL,8,Fentrance to a beach in Cornwall.
OL,10,FSt Austell Coastguard were called to
OL,11,Fthe entrance of Par Beach in St
OL,12,FAustell after reports a person was
OL,13,Fstuck in the mud on Monday, May 11.
OL,15,FThe Coastguard, along with St Austell
OL,16,FCommunity Fire Station, worked to
OL,17,Fextract the individual from the mud,
OL,18,Fwho was found stuck waist deep.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
