PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778655959
OL,3,CPerson rescued after getting stuck
OL,4,Cwaist deep in mud near Cornish beach
OL,6,FThe individual was checked over by the
OL,7,Fambulance service who were waiting on
OL,8,Fthe scene for the rescue to be
OL,9,Fcompleted.
OL,11,FThe road was blocked for some time
OL,12,Fwhile the rescue was carried out.
OL,14,FSt Austell Coastguard said the right
OL,15,Fcall was made to 999, ensuring the
OL,16,Fbest suited emergency service crews
OL,17,Fcould attend the incident.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
