OL,3,CPerson rescued after getting stuck
OL,4,Cwaist deep in mud near Cornish beach
OL,6,FSt Austell Coastguard said: "Tasked to
OL,7,Fa person stuck in the mud by the
OL,8,Fentrance to Par Beach. Once the team
OL,9,Fwere on scene we established a rescue
OL,10,Fplan working along side St Austell
OL,11,FCommunity Fire Station
OL,13,F"The teams worked closely together to
OL,14,Fextract the casualty from the mud and
OL,15,Fhand them over to the waiting
OL,16,Fambulance for checking over.
OL,18,F"The right call to 999 for the
OL,19,Fcoastguard and fire meant the casualty
OL,20,Fgot the right rescue services on scene
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
