OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778655959
OL,3,CPerson rescued after getting stuck
OL,4,Cwaist deep in mud near Cornish beach
OL,6,F"We would like to thank all of the
OL,7,Fpublic who patiently waited as the
OL,8,Froad was blocked whilst we all carried
OL,9,Fout the rescue."
